{"tid":2189400,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"科技股跌勢未完  《FT》：日本軟銀搶購科企期權肇禍","createTime":"2020-09-05T00:56:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T02:27:18.000Z","uid":21622,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"808eb64da4c5fc65356afc8a40383995a5c9bcf4","tid":2189400,"uid":21622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T00:56:26.000Z","msg":"《金融時報》引述消息人士指，日本軟銀集團上月大量搶購美國科股股期權，令部份公司股份出現過去10年以來最大的交易量，更引述有銀行界人士以「危險」形容，是為納指急速升市的背後「巨鯨」，令科技股爆升（Melt-up）。不過今天卻逃不過急跌命運。<br />\n<br />\n真唔真 一間軟銀就操控到市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200904/ETGQMZLXU5CBXIZET3AKSKQHUU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200904%2FETGQMZLXU5CBXIZET3AKSKQHUU%2F&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs44ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=ec1f6b3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200904%2FETGQMZLXU5CBXIZET3AKSKQHUU%2F&h=8e7d795c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200904/ETGQMZLXU5CBXIZET3AKSKQHUU/</a>"},{"pid":"5eac54e86fc6198fe1c92abb020039ca45ea4601","tid":2189400,"uid":21622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T00:58:59.000Z","msg":"FT全文：<a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/75587aa6-1f1f-4e9d-b334-3ff866753fa2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F75587aa6-1f1f-4e9d-b334-3ff866753fa2&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs44ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=47004572\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ft.com/content/75587aa6-1f1f-4e9d-b334-3ff866753fa2</a>"},{"pid":"463ddf444b9277f68fc427e7a956abb24013fb29","tid":2189400,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T01:39:27.000Z","msg":"孫正義呢條撚屌成日搞搞震，上年wework但野都未搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99feae53c00954a852f4002020e7b02567f3102a","tid":2189400,"uid":20368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited